    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "企画コーナー、凄く盛り上がった……\n楽しいイベントもいよいよ大詰め……次が最後の曲……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The special segment was a huge hit…\nThis fun event is finally reaching its finale… the next song is the last one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.8968254089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.0871168822
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.0834919612
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "最後に歌うのは、私達が作ったバレンタインの曲です\n恋愛ソングなんて、ちょっと恥ずかしいけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The final song is a Valentine’s song that we made ourselves.\nA love song is a little embarrassing‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0834919612,
      "endTime": 18.422283617799998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.6156168938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "サニピらしい恋愛ソングってどんな曲だろうって\nみんなで一杯考えて、話し合いながら作ったんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We kept wondering what a “Sunny Peace–style” love song would be like‚\nand made it together through lots of discussions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.6156168938,
      "endTime": 26.4632357599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6565690359
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "みんなと恋の話をするのが新鮮で、楽しくて、おかげで\nドキドキワクワクする私達らしい恋の歌が出来たわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Talking about love with everyone felt fresh and fun‚\nand thanks to that‚ we created a heart-pounding‚ exciting love song that really feels like us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6565690359,
      "endTime": 36.6069548926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vtstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vtstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.8202879589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_01_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "楽しくて幸せな、サニーピースのバレンタインチョコ\nどうぞ召し上がれ――『ラブリー♡♡♡♡♡♡』！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A fun and happy Sunny Peace Valentine’s chocolate—\nplease enjoy it—“Lovely ♡♡♡♡♡♡”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8202879589,
      "endTime": 45.6513310117,
